Name: Artesano Bakery & Café
Description: Located in Monroe Hall, Artesano is the on-campus patisserie offering a wide selection of upscale delicacies, including breakfast pastries and sandwiches, cookies, tarts, and a wide variety of gluten-free, vegan baked goods and specialty created treats. Artesano proudly serves blended frozen drinks, espressos, lattes and cappuccinos from Peet’s Coffee.
